 377, \"to\": 446, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2020 Tokyo Olympic Games\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 417}, {\"ngram\": \"Huston\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 425}, {\"ngram\": \"amedal\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It wasn't my best day skating.\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 479, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my best day skating\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a couple tricks out there that I just could not put down,\\\" he told \\\"CBS Mornings.\\\"\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 572, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 558, \"end\": 561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS\", \"score\": 0.9926338862355307, \"rank\": 0.0038003479511583595, \"text\": \"CBS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a couple tricks\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Huston was born in Davis, California, to his mother Kelle and his father Adeyemi, who is also a skating fanatic.\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 593, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davis,_California\", \"score\": 0.9999999999956799, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Davis, California\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davis,_California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davis,_California\"}, {\"begin\": 593, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davis,_California\", \"score\": 0.9999999999956799, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Davis, California\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davis,_California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davis,_California\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Huston\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 580}, {\"ngram\": \"his mother\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 625}, {\"ngram\": \"Kelle\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"his father\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngram\": \"Adeyemi\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 654}, {\"ngram\": \"a skating fanatic\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 685}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Learning to ride a skateboard in his family was mandatory.\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 745, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a skateboard\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"his family\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 730}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is actually photos of me stacking these random objects that I called my toys on a skateboard.\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"photos\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"these random objects\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"my toys\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"a skateboard\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 846}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was probably, like, two or three years old.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 893, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I was just instantly drawn to it right away,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 953, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Skating is a way of life for Huston, but it did not come easy.\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Skating\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 962}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 971}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"Huston\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 990}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By the age of 10, he was already winning pro competitions.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"pro competitions\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, after an abrupt move to Puerto Rico, Huston disappeared from the skating scene.\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1166, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1111, \"end\": 1122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"score\": 0.9999485762364894, \"rank\": 5.1386940065882314e-05, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an abrupt move\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1107}, {\"ngram\": \"Huston\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1130}, {\"ngram\": \"the skating scene\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Divorce split the family, and Huston remained with his father, who pushed him hard to train.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Divorce\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1174}, {\"ngram\": \"the family\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1191}, {\"ngram\": \"Huston\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"his father\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the fact that I was able to get through all those rough moments as a kid and still come out with that much love for it is the perfect example of, like, how fun skateboarding is.\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1447, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1278}, {\"ngram\": \"all those rough moments\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1333}, {\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1342}, {\"ngram\": \"that much love\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"the perfect example\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"how fun\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's really just an addiction.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just an addiction\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is just, there is nothin' else like it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1525, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothin'\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kelle Huston eventually won custody of her son.\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1574, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kelle Huston\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"custody\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"her son\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Back in California his career exploded.\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1583, \"end\": 1593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.9999822931032388, \"rank\": 1.282532194589497e-05, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1604}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I like to say that his father gave him roots to grow, and I feel like I gave him wings to fly,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1722, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his father\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"roots\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1661}, {\"ngram\": \"wings\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1703}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the family struggled financially until Huston won the first ever street league competition when he was 15 years old.\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1844, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the family\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1738}, {\"ngram\": \"Huston\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1773}, {\"ngram\": \"the first ever street league competition\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The grand prize: $150,000.\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1871, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The grand prize\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That was like, just so much relief and weight being lifted off my shoulders,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1960, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just so much relief\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1908}, {\"ngram\": \"weight\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1919}, {\"ngram\": \"my shoulders\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was finally able to, you know, become my own person.\\\"\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my own person\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now one of the most decorated skateboarders in history, Huston said his failures are the key to his success.\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most decorated skateboarders\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2073}, {\"ngram\": \"Huston\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"his failures\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2099}, {\"ngram\": \"the key\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"his success\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When we put out these video parts that people watch on YouTube or whatever, or they see us skate these contests and land most of our tricks first try, they do not realize that skateboarding is really 90% falling.\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2342, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2185, \"end\": 2192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"score\": 0.9999988579256451, \"rank\": 1.1420756707092218e-06, \"text\": \"YouTube\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these video parts\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2163}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2175}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2204}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2220}, {\"ngram\": \"these contests\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"our tricks\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2269}, {\"ngram\": \"skateboarding\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope you guys show some of the falls in this, because I have taken quite a beating throughout my lifetime.\\\"\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"you guys\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"the falls\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"quite a beating\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"my lifetime\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although he feels the pressure was too much at the Tokyo Games,Parispresents a new opportunity for the 29-year-old.\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2569, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2516}, {\"ngram\": \"a new opportunity\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think Tokyo not going how I wanted to, not skating my best that day, definitely only drives me more to go out there and perform well.\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2580, \"end\": 2585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999809863491006, \"rank\": 1.6751984136213253e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am gonna go out there and do my absolute best.\\\"\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2757, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2024 CBS Interactive Inc. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2766, \"end\": 2786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CBS Interactive Inc.\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(05:06) Copyright \\u00a92025 CBS Interactive Inc. All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2875, \"entitie